LAGOS – Mr. Joseph Chiedu Ugbo, the Managing Director and Chief Executive Officer of Niger Delta Power Holding Company, has been honoured as the Government Agency Administrator of the Year at the ongoing 2021 Independent Awards, taking place at Eko Convention Centre, Eko Hotel and Suites, Victoria Island, Lagos. While receiving the award, he appreciated the management of the newspaper for finding him worthy of receiving the award. He assured Nigerians that as the current henchman – Managing Director and Chief Executive Officer of Niger Delta Power Holding Company- he would continue to do more to ensure that power supply is better than it has always been.